      <scopecontent id="aspace_8f9bc3cf6db011cdbee709a76f00682e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains digital videotapes documenting the 2008 touring production of "The Brig" by Living Theatre. Also included in the collection is a compact disc, printed flyers, brochures, and pamphlets related to the tour.</p>
         <p>Originally presented in 1963 and performed by Living Theatre, the 2007 revival of "The Brig" featured a new version written by Kenneth Brown. It depicts a typical day in a U. S. Marine Corps military prison. In 2008, the troupe's touring production traveled extensively throughout Germany and Italy and was documented by filmmaker Ilya Simakov.</p>
      </scopecontent>
